description:
To try out Mark Rober's Crunch Labs, go to https://crunchlabs.com/HANKGREEN to get your first box, it really is very great!!

I truly loved making this video, and thanks to the TENS OF THOUSANDS of people who helped me make it. I stand by my belief that passenger side is better, and that it should, at the very least, be 50/50. But also, I am happy that we are headed into a future where we won't need them at all anymore.
title: Car Fuel Doors are on THE WRONG SIDE
